Use the standard library
This is how to compare of game and guess:
  Remember that result is []
  Remember that i is 0
  Do this game's length times:
    Remember that g is item i in game
    Remember that x is item i in guess
    When g is x, then:
      Add result to 0
    But, if not:
      When x is less than 0, then:
        Add result to abs of x
      But, if not:
        When g is less than x, then:
          Add result to diff of x and g
        But, if not:
          Add result to diff of g and x
        End when
      End when
    End when
    Increase i by 1
  End do
  The answer is result
Now you know